INSERT INTO movies VALUES('{"title":"Planet 51","year":2009,"cast":["Dwayne Johnson","Jessica Biel","Justin Long","Seann William Scott","Gary Oldman","John Cleese","James Corden","Mathew Horne","Rupert Degas","Alan Marriott","Freddie Benedict"],"genres":["Animated","Comedy","Science Fiction"],"href":"Planet_51","extract":"Planet 51 is a 2009 computer-animated science fiction comedy film directed by Jorge Blanco and co-directed by Javier Abad and Marcos Martínez, from a script by Joe Stillman, based on an original idea by Javier Abad, Jorge Blanco, Marcos Martínez and Ignacio Pérez Dolset. Starring Dwayne Johnson, Jessica Biel, Justin Long, Gary Oldman, Seann William Scott and John Cleese, the film follows an astronaut who lands on an alien planet, as one of the aliens helps him return to his ship while evading the military.","thumbnail":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/72/Planet51movieposter.jpg","thumbnail_width":264,"thumbnail_height":377}');
